pdnAtmStatsMIB.name: pdnAtmStatsMIB

revisions.description: D.GOUGH Added pdnAtmStatTable to count HEC and OCD errors per interface.
Z. Pan o added pdnAtmVclCurrTable - a current 15 minute cells stats and pdnAtmVclHistTable - 96 - 15 minute history cells stats
J. Strain o Initial - VPL and VCL Stats Table

pdnAtmStatsMIB.contactinfo: Paradyne Networks 331 Newman Springs Road Red Bank, NJ 07701 www.paradyne.com General Comments to: mibwg_team@eng.paradyne.com
pdnAtmStatsMIB.description: This MIB Module supports ATM Statistics

pdnAtmVplStatTable.name: pdnAtmVplStatTable
pdnAtmVplStatTable.description: This table contains all statistic counters per VPL. It is used to monitor the usage of the VPL in terms of incoming cells and outgoing cells.

pdnAtmVplStatEntry.name: pdnAtmVplStatEntry
pdnAtmVplStatEntry.description: Each entry in this table represents a VPL.

pdnAtmVplStatIfIndex.name: pdnAtmVplStatIfIndex
pdnAtmVplStatIfIndex.description: A unique value for each interface. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of ifNumber. The value for each interface must remain constant at least from one re-initialization of the entity's network management system to the next re- initialization.

pdnAtmVplStatVpi.name: pdnAtmVplStatVpi
pdnAtmVplStatVpi.description: The VPI value of the VPL.

pdnAtmVplStatTotalCellIns.name: pdnAtmVplStatTotalCellIns
pdnAtmVplStatTotalCellIns.description: The total number of valid ATM cells received by this VPL including both CLP=0 and CLP=1 cells. The cells are counted prior to the application of the traffic policing.

pdnAtmVplStatClp0CellIns.name: pdnAtmVplStatClp0CellIns
pdnAtmVplStatClp0CellIns.description: The number of valid ATM cells received by this VPL with CLP=0. The cells are counted prior to the application of the traffic policing.

pdnAtmVplStatTotalDiscards.name: pdnAtmVplStatTotalDiscards
pdnAtmVplStatTotalDiscards.description: The total number of valid ATM cells discarded by the traffic policing entity. This includes cells originally received with CLP=0 and CLP=1.

pdnAtmVplStatClp0Discards.name: pdnAtmVplStatClp0Discards
pdnAtmVplStatClp0Discards.description: The total number of valid ATM cells received with CLP=0 an discarded by the traffic policing entity.

pdnAtmVplStatTotalCellOuts.name: pdnAtmVplStatTotalCellOuts
pdnAtmVplStatTotalCellOuts.description: The total number of valid ATM cells transmitted by this VPL. This includes both CLP=0 and CLP=1 cells.

pdnAtmVplStatClp0CellOuts.name: pdnAtmVplStatClp0CellOuts
pdnAtmVplStatClp0CellOuts.description: The total number of valid ATM cells transmitted with CLP=0 by this VPL.

pdnAtmVplStatTaggedOuts.name: pdnAtmVplStatTaggedOuts
pdnAtmVplStatTaggedOuts.description: The total number of valid ATM cells tagged by the traffic policing entity from CLP=0 to CLP=1 and transmitted by this VPL.

pdnAtmVclStatTable.name: pdnAtmVclStatTable
pdnAtmVclStatTable.description: This table contains all statistic counters per VCL. It is used to monitor the usage of the VCL in terms of incoming cells and outgoing cells.

pdnAtmVclStatEntry.name: pdnAtmVclStatEntry
pdnAtmVclStatEntry.description: Each entry in this table represents a VCL.

pdnAtmVclStatIfIndex.name: pdnAtmVclStatIfIndex
pdnAtmVclStatIfIndex.description: A unique value for each interface. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of ifNumber. The value for each interface must remain constant at least from one re-initialization of the entity's network management system to the next re- initialization.

pdnAtmVclStatVpi.name: pdnAtmVclStatVpi
pdnAtmVclStatVpi.description: The VPI value of the VCL.

pdnAtmVclStatVci.name: pdnAtmVclStatVci
pdnAtmVclStatVci.description: The VCI value of the VCL.

pdnAtmVclStatTotalCellIns.name: pdnAtmVclStatTotalCellIns
pdnAtmVclStatTotalCellIns.description: The total number of valid ATM cells received by this VCL including both CLP=0 and CLP=1 cells. The cells are counted prior to the application of the traffic policing.

pdnAtmVclStatClp0CellIns.name: pdnAtmVclStatClp0CellIns
pdnAtmVclStatClp0CellIns.description: The number of valid ATM cells received by this VCL with CLP=0. The cells are counted prior to the application of the traffic policing.

pdnAtmVclStatTotalDiscards.name: pdnAtmVclStatTotalDiscards
pdnAtmVclStatTotalDiscards.description: The total number of valid ATM cells discarded by the traffic policing entity. This includes cells originally received with CLP=0 and CLP=1.

pdnAtmVclStatClp0Discards.name: pdnAtmVclStatClp0Discards
pdnAtmVclStatClp0Discards.description: The total number of valid ATM cells received with CLP=0 an discarded by the traffic policing entity.

pdnAtmVclStatTotalCellOuts.name: pdnAtmVclStatTotalCellOuts
pdnAtmVclStatTotalCellOuts.description: The total number of valid ATM cells transmitted by this VCL. This includes both CLP=0 and CLP=1 cells.

pdnAtmVclStatClp0CellOuts.name: pdnAtmVclStatClp0CellOuts
pdnAtmVclStatClp0CellOuts.description: The total number of valid ATM cells transmitted with CLP=0 by this VCL.

pdnAtmVclStatTaggedOuts.name: pdnAtmVclStatTaggedOuts
pdnAtmVclStatTaggedOuts.description: The total number of valid ATM cells tagged by the traffic policing entity from CLP=0 to CLP=1 and transmitted by this VCL.

pdnAtmVclStatRowStatus.name: pdnAtmVclStatRowStatus
pdnAtmVclStatRowStatus.description: This object is used to create a new row or delete an existing row in this table. When a new row is added, statistics are collected for the VCL. Statistics collection is terminated by deletion of the row.

pdnAtmVclCurrTable.name: pdnAtmVclCurrTable
pdnAtmVclCurrTable.description: This table maintains per-TP statistics for the fifteen-minute interval currently being collected.

pdnAtmVclCurrEntry.name: pdnAtmVclCurrEntry
pdnAtmVclCurrEntry.description: An entry in this table for VCL termination points. Each VCL Termination Point automatically has an entry in this table associated with it.

pdnAtmVclCurrElapsedTime.name: pdnAtmVclCurrElapsedTime
pdnAtmVclCurrElapsedTime.description: Amount of time, measured in seconds, that statistics for this entry (the current interval) have been counted.

pdnAtmVclCurrTotalCellIns.name: pdnAtmVclCurrTotalCellIns
pdnAtmVclCurrTotalCellIns.description: The total number of valid ATM cells received by this VCL. This number corresponds to that of toal cells recieved from CPE if this interface is a DSL ATM interface

pdnAtmVclCurrTotalInDiscards.name: pdnAtmVclCurrTotalInDiscards
pdnAtmVclCurrTotalInDiscards.description: The number of discarded received cells.

pdnAtmVclCurrTotalCellOuts.name: pdnAtmVclCurrTotalCellOuts
pdnAtmVclCurrTotalCellOuts.description: The number of cells that have been successfully sent. This number corresponds to that of toal cells transmitted to CPE if this interface is a DSL ATM interface

pdnAtmVclCurrTotalOutDiscards.name: pdnAtmVclCurrTotalOutDiscards
pdnAtmVclCurrTotalOutDiscards.description: The number of discarded transmitted cells since this interval.

pdnAtmVclHistTable.name: pdnAtmVclHistTable
pdnAtmVclHistTable.description: This table maintains per-interface statistics for previous fifteen-minute intervals.

pdnAtmVclHistEntry.name: pdnAtmVclHistEntry
pdnAtmVclHistEntry.description: An entry in History Data table for VCL termination points. Each VCL Termination Point automatically has an entry in this table associated with it.

pdnAtmVclHistIndex.name: pdnAtmVclHistIndex
pdnAtmVclHistIndex.description: A number between 1 and 96, which identifies the interval for which the set of statistics in this entry was collected. The interval identified by 1 is the most recently completed 15 minute interval, and the interval identified by N is the interval immediately preceding the one identified by N-1.

pdnAtmVclHistElapsedTime.name: pdnAtmVclHistElapsedTime
pdnAtmVclHistElapsedTime.description: Amount of Time, measured in units of 0.01 second, that statistics for this entry(the current interval) have been counted.

pdnAtmVclHistTotalCellIns.name: pdnAtmVclHistTotalCellIns
pdnAtmVclHistTotalCellIns.description: The total number of valid ATM cells received by this VCL during this interval. This number corresponds to that of toal cells recieved from CPE if this interface is a DSL ATM interface

pdnAtmVclHistTotalInDiscards.name: pdnAtmVclHistTotalInDiscards
pdnAtmVclHistTotalInDiscards.description: The number of discarded received cells during this interval.

pdnAtmVclHistTotalCellOuts.name: pdnAtmVclHistTotalCellOuts
pdnAtmVclHistTotalCellOuts.description: The number of cells that have been successfully sent during this interval. This number corresponds to that of toal cells transmitted to CPE if this interface is a DSL ATM interface

pdnAtmVclHistTotalOutDiscards.name: pdnAtmVclHistTotalOutDiscards
pdnAtmVclHistTotalOutDiscards.description: The number of discarded transmitted cells during this interval.

pdnAtmStatTable.name: pdnAtmStatTable
pdnAtmStatTable.description: This table contains all statistic counters per interface. It is used to monitor the errors in terms of incoming cells.

pdnAtmStatEntry.name: pdnAtmStatEntry
pdnAtmStatEntry.description: Each entry in this table represents a error count per interface.

pdnAtmStatHECErrors.name: pdnAtmStatHECErrors
pdnAtmStatHECErrors.description: The total number of ATM cells discarded on this interface due to a HEC violation.

pdnAtmStatLCDErrors.name: pdnAtmStatLCDErrors
pdnAtmStatLCDErrors.description: The total number of Loss of Cell Delineataion events (LCD) that occured on this interface.
